 Presidemtial candidate of Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, Atiku Abubakar,  has asked Lauretta Onochie, an aide of President Muhammadu Buhari, for an apology and N500 million for “defamation.” May 20, 2019 In "News" As the All Progressives Congress, APC, questions the citizenship of the presidential candidate of the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, Alhaji Atiku Abubakar, so does the social media aide to President Muhammadu Buhari, Mrs Lauretta Onochie accuses him of planning to destabilize the peace of the country. April 15, 2019 In "News" President Muhammadu Buhari's aide on Social Media, Lauretta Onochie has said that the emergence of former Vice President, Atiku Abubakar as the presidential candidate of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) on Sunday has made the All Progressive Congress work easy. October 7, 2018 In "News"